                "invention-title": [
                    "Process method for removing acidic gas from ammonia-containing acidic condensate and recovering ammonia",
                    "含氨酸性凝液脱除酸性气及氨回收的工艺方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a process method for removing acid gas from ammonia-containing acid condensate and recovering ammonia. The process method is characterized by comprising the following steps: concentrating ammonia-containing gas, removing acid gas, recovering ammonia gas extracted from a side line, refining the ammonia gas and preparing an ammonia product. The acid gas removal load of the pressurized stripping tower and the acid gas removal tower is reduced, and the corrosion risk of an acid medium to a metal equipment pipeline is reduced; the one-time investment cost and the operation cost are greatly reduced; no environment for generating ammonium carbamate exists, and the problem of equipment corrosion is thoroughly solved; the content of acid gas in ammonia gas extracted from the side line is low, the process is simplified, and heat exchange equipment is prevented from being blocked by ammonium salt crystals; the process of step-by-step pressure reduction, cooling and washing is adopted, so that hydrogen sulfide and carbon dioxide in the ammonia gas are dissolved in condensate of step-by-step pressure reduction separators and appear in an ionic state, the dissolved and saturated ammonia gas escapes from the condensate through flash evaporation, and the ammonia gas with relatively high purity is obtained."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种含氨酸性凝液脱除酸性气及氨回收的工艺方法，其特征包括含氨性汽浓缩、脱除酸性气、侧线采出氨气回收、氨气精制、氨产品制取。减少了加压汽提塔和酸性气脱出塔的脱酸性气负荷，降低了酸性介质对金属设备管道的腐蚀风险；一次投资费用和运行成本大幅度降低；没有了氨基甲酸铵生成的环境，彻底解决设备腐蚀问题；侧线采出的氨气中酸性气含量低，简化流程，避免铵盐结晶堵塞换热设备；逐级降压、降温、洗涤的过程，使氨气中硫化氢、二氧化碳溶解在各级降压分离器的冷凝液中以离子态出现，达到溶解饱和的氨气从冷凝液中闪蒸逸出，从而得到纯度较高的氨气。"
                }
            ]
